<h3>Contact</h3>

<p>If you find any bugs or problems in DeskLib, or if you can supply suggestions or code for alterations, additions, or tutorial applications, then please either write to Peter Naulls (<a href="peter@chocky.org">peter@chocky.org</a>), who is the current DeskLib moderator, or raise it on the <a href="http://groups.google.co.uk/group/desklib?hl=en">DeskLib mailing list</a>.</p>

